[{"tablename":"text.sql","select":"Select a.policy_number, a.first_name, a.last_name, a.vin, a.gender, a.vehicle_make, a.vehicle_model, a.vehicle_year
, a.claim_history
,IF(a.claim_history = 0, 100, IF(a.claim_history between 1 and 4, 60, 0)) as claim_history_results 
, b.* 
,cast(b.ts_timestamp / 1000 as timestamp)  as timestamp_dt 
,IF(b.lat_accel between 1.20 AND 1.67, 100, IF(b.lat_accel > 1.68, 25, 50)) as lat_accel_results
,IF(b.long_accel between -0.69 AND 3.0, 100, IF(b.long_accel > 3.1, 25, 50)) as long_accel_results
,IF(b.throttle_pos between 30 AND 70, 100, IF(b.throttle_pos > 71, 25, 50)) as throttle_pos_results
,IF(b.brake_press between 16.55 AND 36.55, 100, IF(b.brake_press > 36.56, 25, 50)) as brake_press_results
,IF(b.steer_ang between 13.15 AND 53.15, 100, IF(b.steer_ang > 53.16, 25, 50)) as steer_ang_results
,IF(b.steer_ang_rate between -100 AND 100, 100, IF(b.steer_ang_rate > 101, 25, 50)) as steer_ang_rate_results
,( IF(b.lat_accel between 1.20 AND 1.67, 100, IF(b.lat_accel > 1.68, 25, 50)) 
    + IF(b.long_accel between -0.69 AND 3.0, 100, IF(b.long_accel > 3.1, 25, 50)) 
    + IF(b.throttle_pos between 30 AND 70, 100, IF(b.throttle_pos > 71, 25, 50))
    + IF(b.brake_press between 16.55 AND 36.55, 100, IF(b.brake_press > 36.56, 25, 50)) 
    + IF(b.steer_ang between 13.15 AND 53.15, 100, IF(b.steer_ang > 53.16, 25, 50))
    + IF(b.steer_ang_rate between -100 AND 100, 100, IF(b.steer_ang_rate > 101, 25, 50)) 
    + IF(a.claim_history = 0, 100, IF(a.claim_history between 1 and 4, 60, 0)) 
    ) / 7
    as driver_avg_score
from default.insured_drivers a
LEFT JOIN default.tm_events_raw b on a.driver_id =
